org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model
Class ScoringScheme

java.lang.Object
  org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model.ScoringScheme

public class ScoringScheme
    
extends java.lang.Object





A Scoring scheme is a predefined set of scores that can be allocated.


When a user wants to score an image, they will have to choose a scoring
scheme and then the score value from that scoring scheme.
